cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SE 

The paper deals with developing adaptive emergency control schemes for power systems using deep reinforcement learning (DRL). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which makes cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category. Finally, the paper discusses the design of an open-source platform for benchmarking DRL algorithms, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering).
